Quest:A Test of Metal

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search
This is a Stub; please help us to expand it by providing verification of prequest

Quest Information


Prequest:
Garden Secret (with Chesea Court access)

Given By: Ernest Haldings

Giver Location: Chelsea Court
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Defeat Gearhead and Collect Internal Gear
Talk to Ernest Haldings
Hand In: Ernest Haldings

Reward:

60
960
Locust Swarm
Banshee
Sunbird
Evil Snowman
Nature's Wrath
Cyclops
Storm Shark
Gearhead Destroyer
Vampire
Immolate
Ice Wyvern
Seraph
Cyclops Minion
Kraken

Leads to:

The Key Component

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to A Test of Metal should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.
